    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-08-27T04:21:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-08-27T04:21:00-05:00" n="805"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d805">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/5117: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Commissioner at Helsingfors</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Haynes</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Helsingfors</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-27T11:00:00+01:39">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 27, 1919, 11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>389. Northern Russian Army Corps after receiving its new supply of English tanks
                    has been driven back and Pskov captured by Bolsheviks, the probable result being
                    that Esthonia may make peace with Soviet or be driven into Bolshevikism by the
                    harassing of <persName corresp="#p_GGSH1">Gough</persName>
                    <note n="43" xml:id="d805fn43">Lt. Gen. Sir <persName corresp="#p_GGSH1">Hubert
                            Gough</persName>, chief of the British mission to the Baltic
                        States.</note> and <persName>Judenitch</persName>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Haynes</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
